    "While CoT successfully determines the correct answer, it fails to acknowledge the mention of \"Amish cousins\", thus exhibiting a tenuous connection to the question.",
    "Unexpectedly, Self-Refine underperforms compared to other baselines, aligning with (Huang et al., 2023) who highlight the drawbacks of selfcorrection in reasoning tasks.",
